msgid "What is a Dina?"
msgstr "Inona ny Dina ?"

msgid "In Malagasy culture, the Dina is a community agreement — a set of rules and commitments freely accepted by all members of a community to live together with respect and solidarity (Fihavanana)."
msgstr "Ao amin'ny kolontsaina malagasy, ny Dina dia fifanarahana iombonana — andian-dàlana sy fanekempihavanana nekena an-tsitrapo nataon'ny mpikambana rehetra amin'ny vondrona iray mba hiara-monina amin'ny fanajana sy ny Fihavanana."

# ── Kabary ──
msgid "Kabary numérique"
msgstr "Kabary nomerika"

msgid "The Kabary is a traditional Malagasy oral art form — a structured speech that opens with a salutation, develops ideas with imagery and proverbs, and closes with a blessing. Share your thoughts in this timeless format."
msgstr "Ny Kabary dia karazan-kira Malagasy nentim-paharazana — resaka voamboatra izay manomboka amin'ny fiarahabana, mamolavola hevitra amin'ny sary sy ohabolana, ary mihidy amin'ny tsodrano. Zarao ny sainao amin'ity endrika mandrakizay ity."

msgid "Title (optional)"
msgstr "Lohateny (tsy voatery)"

msgid "optional"
msgstr "tsy voatery"

msgid "Title of your Kabary…"
msgstr "Lohateny ny Kabarynao…"

msgid "Give your Kabary a memorable title."
msgstr "Omeo lohateny tsy hadinoina ny Kabarynao."

msgid "Opening salutation. Address your audience respectfully."
msgstr "Fiarahabana fanombohana. Miteny amin'ny maneho fanajana amin'ny mpifanatrika."

msgid "Tompokolahy, Tompokovavy, ry havana… (Respected men, respected women, dear kin…)"
msgstr "Tompokolahy, Tompokovavy, ry havana…"

msgid "Introduction — set the context and purpose of your speech."
msgstr "Fampidirana — asehoy ny tontolon-kevitra sy ny tanjona ny resaka."

msgid "Why I speak today, the occasion that brings us together…"
msgstr "Maninona aho no miteny androany, ny antony namorona antsika…"

msgid "The heart of the Kabary — your main message, ideas and reflections. (Required)"
msgstr "Fo-po ny Kabary — ny hafatrao, ny hevitrao ary ny fisainanao. (Ilaina)"

msgid "Develop your thoughts, ideas, stories…"
msgstr "Ampitomboy ny sainao, hevitrao, tantaranao…"

msgid "A Malagasy proverb to illuminate your message."
msgstr "Ohabolana malagasy mampihazava ny hafatrao."

msgid "Ny teny mamy, toy ny tantely… (Sweet words, like honey…)"
msgstr "Ny teny mamy, toy ny tantely…"

msgid "Closing words, blessing for all…"
msgstr "Teny farany, tsodrano ho an'ny rehetra…"

msgid "Closing — conclusion, blessing, thanks."
msgstr "Fanidiana — famaranana, tsodrano, fisaorana."

msgid "Publish Kabary"
msgstr "Hamoaka Kabary"

msgid "Preview"
msgstr "Fijery mialoha"

msgid "The main content (Vato misaina) is required."
msgstr "Ny votoatin-dresaka (Vato misaina) dia ilaina."

